{"tid":481951,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"月入31K, 想平平地買部車仔過下手癮","createTime":"2017-11-27T16:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T02:17:49.000Z","uid":52891,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0b9d86ecee9d1d8f5f50ad18389a3b2871e02ea7","tid":481951,"uid":52891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:06:18.000Z","msg":"其實返工太近唔會渣<br />\n平時又唔會話好多偏遠地方想去 (如果將來有女友另計)<br />\n但辛苦考左個牌唔玩下好似有d曬<br />\n所以想平平買部過下手癮<br />\n無聊周圍兜下散下心<br />\n或者遲d同女友遊車河<br />\n自細一上左人地私家車、的士就又種講唔出既?滿足感?安全感?興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家有咩意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5b67e8e471928b9cc566039c8f5aaba0908aa8","tid":481951,"uid":136252,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:11:27.000Z","msg":"Audi tt"},{"pid":"199efa45e2e5d9bb6112195d4ab949524c2b7dbd","tid":481951,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"31k <br />\n有幾多閒錢<br />\n使唔使比家用<br />\n同屋企住定自己搬出去住<br />\n屋企停車場貴唔貴"},{"pid":"4556671aa80e5cbe54e6e36faea4dcc117f46b8d","tid":481951,"uid":52891,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>31k <br />\n有幾多閒錢<br />\n使唔使比家用<br />\n同屋企住定自己搬出去住<br />\n屋企停車場貴唔貴</blockquote><br />\n每月儲到17-20k<br />\n6k家用 同屋企人住<br />\n車位應該貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7413681c737c098d88e68b5c1df5c4783817f50a","tid":481951,"uid":52891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6df15ce1d2faf0015876589b449b04dec6f21bb","tid":481951,"uid":46595,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"新牌仔唔建議買新車<br />\n是但買架golf / jazz 二手玩下先啦<br />\n幾萬蚊又唔算大食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到你發現原來部車一個星期都係開得一兩日要每月比成5000~6000供奉<br />\n你就會賣車保平安架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdc8bf7f2440f0b5d14321d77fcbfe38bf85af1","tid":481951,"uid":771,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新牌仔唔建議買新車<br />\n是但買架golf / jazz 二手玩下先啦<br />\n幾萬蚊又唔算大食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到你發現原來部車一個星期都係開得一兩日要每月比成5000~6000供奉<br />\n你就會賣車保平安架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n玩一兩年洗十零廿萬唔緊要既<br />\n<br />\n到你第時一買就買死成世七人車你就真係後悔<br />\n<br />\n後生玩兩年自己鐘意既型號係幾值得"},{"pid":"1968d9e039205ecf90bd1e86740b03e28fe84447","tid":481951,"uid":13878,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:36:28.000Z","msg":"養車唔係問題<br />\n不過搵左車位先<br />\n<br />\n因為我試過有架車而搵唔到車位, 係貴一貴都無, 勁頭痕<br />\n<br />\n如果搵到車位而又覺得價錢OK, 咪去馬咯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於買咩車, 個個人都有唔同偏好, 好難講你鐘意咩~<br />\n<br />\n我自己第一架車係2014年買既<br />\n當時岩岩考到牌, 買左架二手2005年既smart fortwo<br />\n好唔好就見人見智, 但換左3架車, 仍然最鐘意呢架"},{"pid":"d8d2d20b580ec4d76e42f0bc85b100761a2b3b71","tid":481951,"uid":81575,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:47:20.000Z","msg":"忍下手，儲吓錢先<br />\n<br />\n過來人意見，當年同你搵一樣多時，用了每月9000養車，而家好後悔"},{"pid":"3070fe5f9f4442c6b7cc6fa082b383f2e5b0b4aa","tid":481951,"uid":130365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:49:21.000Z","msg":"住邊區？<br />\n你平時返工又唔渣 ，姐係一星期先渣1-2次"},{"pid":"2a26c7bc2736b8053ff6181a33ca74064f0a7ba1","tid":481951,"uid":130365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住邊區？<br />\n你平時返工又唔渣 ，姐係一星期先渣1-2次</blockquote><br />\n你成個月計先渣5-8次 要比最少5千養車，重未計突發/壞車果啲 你自己諗下抵唔抵囉"},{"pid":"6e7deff0eca1caeb16af3843b4e6aa19e4796673","tid":481951,"uid":63,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T07:11:43.000Z","msg":"31k 買架靚26算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a74fe87ea44ed8a37ab1aabb046fbfabb74bc7","tid":481951,"uid":73,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>31k 買架靚26算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n月入唔係budget 喎"},{"pid":"29ba5bef1093fcbc4d34816333aef3089deb5f49","tid":481951,"uid":90814,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>31k 買架靚26算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n月入唔係budget 喎</blockquote><br />\n佢個名"},{"pid":"8caa51a0d83008f0a67793f884cbd794eba1a02e","tid":481951,"uid":127583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"其實平時聽人講養車 其實主要係啲咩 油錢 車保？"},{"pid":"8dd38751ba20e4726de3d9c6397cd0679a923454","tid":481951,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>31k 買架靚26算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n月入唔係budget 喎</blockquote><br />\n佢個名</blockquote><br />\n係月入呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b342e8bf615781c5e52d0c2204f7754cc96de8","tid":481951,"uid":4207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:51:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實平時聽人講養車 其實主要係啲咩 油錢 車保？</blockquote><br />\n油車場牌費燕梳消耗品維修雜費等等"},{"pid":"98a0160be6b78b1f8e884fb8296e9b1f81d78226","tid":481951,"uid":32028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:55:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>31k 買架靚26算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n月入唔係budget 喎</blockquote><br />\n佢個名</bloc